Iran says it did not request talks with the United States in Doha, directly rejecting President Trump’s claim that Tehran sought a meeting.

Iranian officials added that no negotiations with the U.S. are scheduled in the coming days, stressing that the delegation’s trip to Qatar is only for follow up discussions on the implementation of the MoU and not for talks with American officials.
